'''喜馬拉雅兔'''（Himalayan rabbit），又稱為'''五黑兔'''，是[[家兔|家兔]]的一個[[品種_(動物)|品種]]。喜馬拉雅兔出生時全身均為白色，六個月後其鼻子、耳朵、前腳、後腳與尾巴等部位毛色會轉為黑色，其他部位則維持白色<Ref>
{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=FTB-CgAAQBAJ&pg=PT59&lpg=PT59&dq=Himalayan+rabbit+smut&source=bl&ots=IoOTbyLpnq&sig=RQhsM5Nrd-TsqqpfeNbDWrX3iR0&hl=zh-TW&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwjj-N3L38veAhWBJnwKHbedBfw4FBDoATADegQICRAB#v=onepage&q=Himalayan%20rabbit%20smut&f=false|title=Practical Rabbit Keeping - Rabbits for Pets and Profit|author=George A. Townsend|publisher=Read Books Ltd|year=2013|isbn=1473390087|access-date=2018-11-11|archive-date=2019-08-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190802220921/https://books.google.com/books?id=FTB-CgAAQBAJ&pg=PT59&lpg=PT59&dq=Himalayan+rabbit+smut&source=bl&ots=IoOTbyLpnq&sig=RQhsM5Nrd-TsqqpfeNbDWrX3iR0&hl=zh-TW&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwjj-N3L38veAhWBJnwKHbedBfw4FBDoATADegQICRAB#v=onepage&q=Himalayan%20rabbit%20smut&f=false|dead-url=no}}
</ref>，造成此現象的原因是其參與[[黑色素|黑色素]]合成途徑的一種[[酵素|酵素]]在攝氏33度以上的溫度會失去活性，只有上述部位因體溫低於攝氏33度，使該酵素正常運作而得以合成黑色素，因此毛色為黑色<ref>{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=EXNFwB-O-WUC&pg=PA163&dq=Himalayan+Rabbit&hl=zh-TW&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwjf6PmR1sveAhUEL30KHXADDXQQ6AEIMzAB#v=onepage&q=Himalayan%20Rabbit&f=false|title=Biology: Concepts and Applications without Physiology|author=Cecie Starr|page=163|publisher=Cengage Learning|year=2007|isbn=0495381500|access-date=2018-11-11|archive-date=2019-07-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190730191526/https://books.google.com/books?id=EXNFwB-O-WUC&pg=PA163&dq=Himalayan+Rabbit&hl=zh-TW&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwjf6PmR1sveAhUEL30KHXADDXQQ6AEIMzAB#v=onepage&q=Himalayan%20Rabbit&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

喜馬拉雅兔的起源目前仍不清楚，亦無明確證據證明此品種起源自[[喜馬拉雅山|喜馬拉雅山區]]<ref name=history/>，許多人認為它可能源於[[中國|中國]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.himalayanrabbit.com/copy-of-archived-breed-history|title=Majestic Beauty of The Ages|publisher=The American Himalayan Rabbit Association|author=Jacinta Taulbee|year=2016|accessdate=2018-11-11|archive-date=2020-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200927075049/https://www.himalayanrabbit.com/copy-of-archived-breed-history|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此品種在世界各地被廣泛繁殖，擁有許多別名，是歷史最為悠久的[[家兔|家兔]]品種之一<ref name=history>{{cite web|url=https://www.himalayanrabbit.com/breed-history|title=The History of the Himalayan Rabbit: Everything We Know|publisher=The American Himalayan Rabbit Association|year=2016|accessdate=2018-11-11|archive-date=2019-08-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190802174802/https://www.himalayanrabbit.com/breed-history|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

